name: Joyride #04
description:
Imagine a ride through the city, your favourite night club just closed, you're still hyped but kinda trash. The city is empty, just some lonely cars. You're feeling the night, you're feeling the wind, it's all perfect ... 

Joyride is a series of 4 pictures.
Location: Frankfurt am Main
Car: 64er Mustang
Model: Alessia
